author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Andor might have gotten off to a rocky start with Season 2, but boy did it redeem itself with the last few episodes. This may be the best Star Wars we'll ever get from Disney. 

Check out the Saints and Sinners comic I've been working on with The Rippaverse: https://rippaverse.com/collections/saints-sinners-1/
title: Andor Finally Got Me
